div1.p:
Q. Did any person come afterwards as the owner - A. Yes;
James Knight
came with Wittam; he came as a Russia captain; he told me he was just arrived from Russia, and these skins I had seen in the morning, he had sent them as a sample. There was a black cub bear skin, a swan skin, and a Russia white hare. He said his vessel was in the river. I asked to see all that he had; he said he would bring the remainder. I never saw him afterwards until he was in custody.
